review_title: How is this game not more known?
one_reviews_text: It is so fun.  My fiance and I played together with the bots and it was a lot of fun.  The bots are pretty tough actually .  Has a few different modes rather than just deathmatch.  King of the Hill is one of the best.  Great game, and free!
It is a good game and it is fun but i could not find a online match i could only play it with bots. The bots have difficulty so they are not just easy but fun game it just beed a bigger player base
